Sentencas: La0.6Sr0.4Ru0.9Mg0.1O3-delta (LSRM) powder was prepared by co-precipitation method using ammonium carbonate solution and nitrate solutions.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrical conductivity of La0.6Sr0.4Ru0.9Mg0.1O3-δ perovskite solid solution

Sentencas: The freeze-dried suspension was decomposed at 1000 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrical conductivity of La0.6Sr0.4Ru0.9Mg0.1O3-δ perovskite solid solution

Sentencas: The obtained LSRM powder was sintered in air at 1200 degrees C for 4 h to measure the electrical conductivity.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrical conductivity of La0.6Sr0.4Ru0.9Mg0.1O3-δ perovskite solid solution

Sentencas: The LSRM solid solution, which was stable in the temperature range front 1000 to 1500 degrees C in air, was referred to an orthorhombic structure.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrical conductivity of La0.6Sr0.4Ru0.9Mg0.1O3-δ perovskite solid solution

Sentencas: The measured true density of LSRM powder was close to the density calculated using X-ray diffraction data.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrical conductivity of La0.6Sr0.4Ru0.9Mg0.1O3-δ perovskite solid solution

Sentencas: No chemical reaction occurred between LSRM and Gd-doped ceria electrolyte at 1000 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrical conductivity of La0.6Sr0.4Ru0.9Mg0.1O3-δ perovskite solid solution

Sentencas: The electronic conductivity of LSRM measured by a four-terminal DC method was 423 and 361 S.cm(-1) at 300 and 800 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Synthesis and electrical conductivity of La0.6Sr0.4Ru0.9Mg0.1O3-δ perovskite solid solution
